To get this running on heroku

install the heroku toolkit.

    https://toolbelt.heroku.com/

Type the following with your credentials

    heroku login

fork the project

type the following inside the project folder
  
    heroku create

then type 

    git push heroku master

The last line of the push will give a url.    Something like

    http://still-bayou-2884.herokuapp.com

It should show Hello World! with is the contents of the public/index.html
